metadata.name: The God's Eye
metadata.description:
NFT Art by SeñOriva 

 Everything is controlled by a program that follows certain laws of the Universe.
 Does it have an author?
 And is there anyone who supervises the performance of this program?

 Or maybe it's the same character?

 And who is He in relation to Me?
 And if I can observe the ongoing performance of this program, maybe I am He?

 Laws, things, system, control, world order...
 Does it all exist at least somewhere other than my consciousness?
 Or not?

 When you are an observer, endowed with the "God’s Eye", you begin to control the planet and civilizations with which you interact, simply observing them.
 After all, the observer inevitably affects the object of observation.

 Observe & Enjoy

Size of canvas (oil) : 100*90
Size of video: 5247х5835 
Original track: mp3 
Year: 2022
